  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We investigate the effects of repeated NAC administration on glutamate concentrations in the
      anterior cingulate cortex (ACC), on neurocognitive functioning, and on neuro-inflammatory
      parameters in adult cannabis-dependent individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
